  root@number:~# time perf test "Parsing of PMU event table metrics"
   10.3: Parsing of PMU event table metrics                            : Ok
   10.4: Parsing of PMU event table metrics with fake PMUs             : Ok

  real	0m9.277s
  user	0m9.979s
  sys	0m0.055s
